ri-dimensional photo of a rock-faced man in a merchant spaceman's uniform with a neatly trimmed red beard in his room on Venus, and that this image haunts him in his sleep. It is possible that the red-bearded man is Jake's father or another member of her group of spacemen who operate beyond Mars and have established a base on an asteroid.">
